sub_title: Physics Teacher, Math Teacher at Joke Smit College
summary:
- Trainee at "Eerst de Klas", secondary school teacher in Mathematics and Physics

- Graduated student at De Bildung Academie (2016)

- Graduated student Applied Physics at Delft University of Technology (2015)

- Full time position as commissioner of education/lustrum of the Study Association for Applied Physics at the TU Delft (2012)
